prompts.frontCover:
Greeting card front cover, a whimsical and funny beach scene in a vibrant watercolor style.

An illustrated cartoon version of Lao Lao, wearing her light blue sweatshirt and black pants, is dramatically buried up to her neck in sand, looking playfully annoyed with sand in her hair. An illustrated cartoon version of Jordan, wearing his brown hoodie and dark pants, stands proudly beside her, holding a small plastic toy shovel and bucket, beaming with a mischievous grin as if he just finished his "masterpiece."

The beach is idyllic and stylized with soft, flowing watercolor washes. The sand is a warm golden yellow, the ocean is a mix of turquoise and cerulean blue with soft white wave crests, and the sky is a bright, sunny wash of pale blue and soft white clouds. A few cartoon seagulls fly overhead wearing tiny party hats, and a cheerful cartoon crab scuttles by, also wearing a miniature party hat and carrying a tiny birthday gift wrapped with a bow.

Centered in the sky above them, written in a beautiful, flowing, and easily readable handwritten cursive script, is the text: "Happy Birthday Lao Lao". The text is rendered in a dark teal color.

The overall composition is lighthearted, charming, and humorous, focusing on the playful interaction between the couple. The art style is flat 2D with soft edges and blended colors characteristic of watercolor painting.
